[In the absence of information on the clinical presentation of the cases,
or information on the incubation period it is hazardous to attempt to
define the etiology of this outbreak. An article in the Kansas City
Star (<http://www.kansascity.com/mld/kansascity/3657414.htm> mentioned
that the health department would have to suspend the investigation until
Monday, as most participants registered giving their work contact
information and hence they were unable to contact participants for the
investigation. More information on this outbreak from official sources
would be appreciated when available. - Mod.MPP]
